nodes.text: A fleet technician served onboard the Xyston-class Star Destroyer Derriphan and under Captain Chesille Sabrond during the Battle of Exegol. The fleet technician was killed when the Resistance destroyed the Derriphan.
The fleet technician first appeared in the 2019 film Star Wars: Episode IX The Rise of Skywalker, the final installment of the Star Wars sequel trilogy.
